%% Enterprise AI — Event & Message Flow
%% What: All async communication paths (Redis pub/sub, WebSocket, Celery)
%% Where: Between API, workers, graph, and client
%% Why: Shows how progress is tracked, replayed, and persisted across disconnects

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as React SPA
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant CEL as Celery Worker
    participant GRAPH as LangGraph Pipeline
    participant REDIS as Redis
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant WS as WebSocket Handler
    participant CLAUDE as Claude API

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Upload & Dispatch ═══

    UI->>+API: POST /upload (multipart file)
    API->>API: G1-lite: magic bytes + size check
    API->>PG: INSERT uploads (upload_id, filename, sha256)
    API-->>-UI: {upload_id, format, filename}

    UI->>+API: POST /run {upload_id, config_overrides}
    API->>PG: INSERT batches (batch_id, status=QUEUED)
    API->>CEL: celery.send_task(run_dynafit_pipeline)
    API-->>-UI: {batch_id, ws_url, status: "queued"}

    UI->>+WS: WS connect /ws/progress/{batch_id}
    WS->>REDIS: HGETALL batch:{batch_id}
    WS-->>UI: replay persisted phase states (catch-up)
    WS->>REDIS: SUBSCRIBE progress:{batch_id}

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Phase 1: Ingestion ═══

    CEL->>+GRAPH: graph.invoke(initial_state)
    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseStartEvent{phase=1, name="ingestion"}
    REDIS->>WS: forward event
    WS-->>UI: {"type": "phase_start", "phase": 1}
    REDIS->>REDIS: HSET batch:{batch_id} phases.1.started

    GRAPH->>GRAPH: Parse → G3 → G2 → Atomize
    GRAPH->>CLAUDE: atomization LLM call
    CLAUDE-->>GRAPH: atoms[]

    loop For each progress chunk
        GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB StepProgressEvent{step, completed, total}
        REDIS->>WS: forward
        WS-->>UI: {"type": "step_progress", "pct": 45}
    end

    GRAPH->>PG: Checkpoint (full state after Phase 1)
    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseCompleteEvent{atoms_produced, atoms_validated, atoms_flagged}
    REDIS->>REDIS: HSET batch:{batch_id} phases.1.complete

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Phase 2–3: Retrieval + Matching ═══

    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseStartEvent{phase=2, name="retrieval"}
    Note right of GRAPH: Parallel 3-source retrieval<br/>(Qdrant + Docs + pgvector)<br/>asyncio.Semaphore(12)

    loop Per atom batch
        GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB StepProgressEvent
        REDIS->>WS: forward
        WS-->>UI: progress update
    end

    GRAPH->>PG: Checkpoint (state after Phase 2)
    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseCompleteEvent{phase=2}

    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseStartEvent{phase=3, name="matching"}
    Note right of GRAPH: Pure compute: numpy + rapidfuzz<br/>No LLM calls, no infra calls
    GRAPH->>PG: Checkpoint (state after Phase 3)
    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseCompleteEvent{phase=3}

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Phase 4: Classification ═══

    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseStartEvent{phase=4, name="classification"}

    par Parallel LLM calls (ThreadPool, max_workers=10)
        GRAPH->>CLAUDE: FAST_TRACK (1 call, T=0.0)
        CLAUDE-->>GRAPH: tool-use response
    and
        GRAPH->>CLAUDE: DEEP_REASON call 1 (T=0.3)
        GRAPH->>CLAUDE: DEEP_REASON call 2 (T=0.3)
        GRAPH->>CLAUDE: DEEP_REASON call 3 (T=0.3)
        CLAUDE-->>GRAPH: majority vote
    and
        GRAPH->>CLAUDE: GAP_CONFIRM (1 call, T=0.0)
        CLAUDE-->>GRAPH: tool-use response
    end

    loop Per classified atom
        GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB ClassificationEvent{atom_id, verdict, confidence}
        REDIS->>WS: forward
        WS-->>UI: live classification result
    end

    GRAPH->>PG: Checkpoint (state after Phase 4)
    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseCompleteEvent{phase=4}

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Phase 5A: Sanity Gate + HITL Decision ═══

    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB PhaseStartEvent{phase=5, name="validation"}
    GRAPH->>GRAPH: G10-lite sanity checks + confidence filter + anomaly flags

    alt Flagged items exist
        GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB ReviewRequiredEvent{flagged_count, flagged_atom_ids}
        REDIS->>WS: forward
        WS-->>UI: {"type": "review_required", "count": 7}
        GRAPH->>PG: Checkpoint (interrupt state — graph frozen)
        GRAPH-->>CEL: status="interrupted"
        CEL->>REDIS: PUB PhaseCompleteEvent{phase=5, status="awaiting_review"}

        Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Human Review Loop ═══

        UI->>+API: GET /review (fetch flagged queue)
        API->>PG: SELECT flagged atoms + evidence
        API-->>-UI: flagged_items[] with ai_classification, rationale, evidence

        loop For each flagged atom
            UI->>+API: POST /review/{atom_id} {decision: APPROVE|OVERRIDE}
            API->>PG: INSERT review_items
            API-->>-UI: {final_classification, remaining: N}
        end

        UI->>+API: POST /review/complete
        API->>CEL: celery.send_task(resume, overrides_dict)
        API-->>-UI: {status: "resuming"}

        Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Phase 5B: Merge + Report (Resumed) ═══

        CEL->>+GRAPH: graph.invoke(Command(resume=overrides))
        Note right of GRAPH: Resumes from exact checkpoint
    else No flagged items
        Note right of GRAPH: Skip interrupt, proceed directly
    end

    GRAPH->>GRAPH: Merge overrides → Build batch → Write CSVs
    GRAPH->>PG: Write fitments + pgvector embeddings (for future Source C)

    GRAPH->>REDIS: PUB CompleteEvent{fit_count, gap_count, report_url}
    REDIS->>REDIS: HSET batch:{batch_id} status=complete
    REDIS->>WS: forward terminal event
    WS-->>UI: {"type": "complete", "report_url": "..."}
    WS->>WS: close WebSocket

    GRAPH-->>-CEL: final state
    CEL->>PG: UPDATE batches SET status=COMPLETE

    Note over UI,CLAUDE: ═══ Reconnect Scenario ═══

    UI->>+WS: WS reconnect /ws/progress/{batch_id}
    WS->>REDIS: HGETALL batch:{batch_id}
    WS-->>UI: replay all persisted phases (full catch-up)
    WS->>REDIS: SUBSCRIBE progress:{batch_id}
    Note right of WS: Client sees complete history<br/>even after disconnect
